paragraphs.title: Copy data to HDFS

%sh

hadoop fs -rm -r -f /tmp/ml-100k

hadoop fs -mkdir /tmp/ml-100k

hadoop fs -put /tmp/u.data /tmp/ml-100k/
hadoop fs -put /tmp/u.item /tmp/ml-100k/
